  "prompt": "What are some small restaurant chains in Dallas? (under 10 locations)",
  "response": "Here are a few small restaurant chains in the Dallas area that have fewer than 10 locations:\n\n1. **Cane Rosso** - Known for its Neapolitan-style pizzas, Cane Rosso has several locations around Dallas.\n\n2. **Meso Maya** - This restaurant offers authentic Mexican and Mayan cuisine and has a handful of locations in the Dallas area.\n\n3. **Mellow Mushroom** - Although part of a larger chain, the Dallas area has a limited number of locations offering their signature pizzas.\n\n4. **Bread Winners Caf\u00e9 & Bakery** - Known for breakfast, brunch, and bakery items, this local favorite has a few locations in and around Dallas.\n\n5. **Velvet Taco** - Known for its creative take on tacos, Velvet Taco has several locations in the Dallas area but remains a relatively small chain.\n\n6. **Rodeo Goat** - Famous for its inventive burgers, Rodeo Goat has a few locations including in the Dallas area.\n\n7. **The Rustic** - A popular spot for live music, food, and drinks, The Rustic has locations in Dallas and nearby areas.\n\nThese chains are popular for their unique offerings and local flair, with each having a distinct identity that resonates well with Dallas diners.",
